\v 3 And you shall leave through breaches \add in the wall\add*, each one in front of her. You will be dragged off toward Harmon,”\f + \fr 4:3 \ft The meaning of this Hebrew word is uncertain \f* ⸤declares⸥\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Literally “a declaration of” \f* Yahweh. 
