\v 9 And then in that day,” ⸤declares⸥\f + \fr 8:9 \ft Literally “a declaration of” \f* my Lord Yahweh, “I\f + \fr 8:9 \ft Literally “and I” \f* will make the sun go down at noon and I will darken the land on a day of light. 
